Package: oraltags
Type: Package
Title: Oral Data Tagger and Prosody Explorer
Version: 2.2.0
Authors@R: person("Adrián", "Cabedo-Nebot", role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "cabedoadrian@gmail.com",
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3881-9308"))
Description: Shiny application for the linguistic annotation and
    acoustic-prosodic analysis of oral corpora from audio and Praat TextGrids:
    navigation by intonation groups, automatic prosodic metrics (F0, intensity,
    speech rate), configurable annotation scheme, corpus descriptives and
    inter-annotator agreement (Cohen/Fleiss kappa, Krippendorff alpha).
    Launch it with run_app(); user data is stored in the standard per-user
    folder (tools::R_user_dir). Bundles audio + TextGrid samples to try the
    application. Interface available in English and Spanish.
License: GPL-3
URL: https://acabedo.github.io/oraltags/, https://github.com/acabedo/oraltags
